      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful, regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the upholstery shows light, natural softening but is free of any rips or significant stains. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, is fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, backed by a complete folder of service records. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It has recently undergone a multi-point inspection and a fresh oil change, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. If you are looking for a vehicle that balances pride of ownership with mechanical integrity, this is an exceptional choice.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
