      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This F87 M2 is powered by the N55B30T0 3.0L twin-scroll turbocharged inline-six, delivering a robust 365 hp and 343 lb-ft of torque via a short-throw 6-speed manual gearbox. The drivetrain is anchored by the Active M Differential, an electronically controlled multi-plate limited-slip unit that optimizes traction and directional stability. The chassis features lightweight aluminum front and rear axles derived from the M4, ensuring precise kinematic response. This example has been upgraded with an aluminum charge pipe to address the factory plastic failure point and has undergone a recent walnut blasting of the intake valves to maintain optimal volumetric efficiency. Mechanically sound with crisp gear synchronization and a linear power band, it represents a purist-spec driver\u2019s tool.",
